entries.s_32: Before you even ask, the prototype was stolen. You will have to recover it from the thieves before they can fence it. They let slip that their hideout is somewhere outside of Narmle.
entries.s_34: Unbelievable that I would be robbed just as I was to deliver the prototype. Though on second thought, maybe that isn't so unbelievable at that. Time to increase security.
